            <span class="block text-red-300 mt-2">Sound Quality Is Audible</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl">{description}</p>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-2">The music studio reality:</p>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-sm">Indie artist searching "recording studio full production" visits 18 studio websites. 13 have equipment lists only, no sound samples, unclear pricing, difficult booking process. 1 modern site with before/after audio samples prominently, equipment specs visible, transparent package pricing, easy booking system. Guess where they book? For studios, audible quality = sound capability = book session. Your website = 24/7 studio tour that never closes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg="[#FEF2F2]">
