        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">What nobody tells music studios about websites</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Audio samples visible: 6x more bookings</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Studio had equipment list only. Added before/after audio samples prominently. Month 1: 6x more session bookings. Hear quality = confident = book.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
