            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Package pricing visible: 53% smoother sales</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added "Full Production: $2,500/day" prominently. Month 1: 53% smoother qualification. Pricing = can afford = book.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Client testimonials visible: 43% more trust</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added artist testimonials with album clips prominently. Month 1: 43% more confident bookings. Social proof = trust = book.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile studio browsing: 79% check on phones</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Music = mobile browsing. Non-responsive audio player = skip this studio. Mobile-optimized = hear samples = book.</p>
            </div>
